Class SetupResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epita.creeps.given.vo.response.SetupResponse
  • public final class SetupResponse
extends Object
    Response VO class for server setup. Sent as a member of InitResponse upon a player connection.

      • maxMissesPerPlayer

        @Min(0L)
public final @javax.validation.constraints.Min(0L) int maxMissesPerPlayer
        Number of allowed misses for the player. Every miss on a unit increment the global player misses counter. Once reached, any miss on any agent will terminate it.
